**PLEASE UPVOTE if you like** 😁 **If you have any question, feel free to ask.** 
* Key Point
	* `pre` is the sum of prefix of path from root to current node **NOT Inclusive**
* Top-Down
	* DFS Traverse the tree from root to every leaf, once we arrived at a leaf, add the sum of path from root to leaf to the final answer
* Bottom-Up
	* After arriving at a leaf, return the sum of path bottom-up to the root.

![image](https://assets.leetcode.com/users/images/2686b5d7-bc15-42c6-96ac-55d95119c67e_1641884337.480884.png)



**Top-Down**
**C++**
