**Idea:**
We treaverse the tree, and concatenate the binary numbers to one string in `sum`.
When we reach a leaf node, we calculate the value of the binary string and add to `res`.

**Time Complexity:** O(n)
**Space Complexity:** O(1) without considering recursive stack, O(height) with recursive call stack.

**C++:**
