##### Implementing a simple recursive pre-order function with an array for strings made by traversing till each leaf-node.
With each recursion-call check if current-node is a leaf:
	If yes, then append currently created string value to the res-array.
	If no, then push left and right child nodes onto the stack.

Finally just convert your string arrays into decimal using the int function and sum up the res-array.
